<subSubSection id="C33148A4FFC4FFE6FF3D8175FB2FF85C" pageId="12" pageNumber="102" type="discussion">
<subSubSection id="C33148A4FFC4FFE6FF3D8175FE2CFC8A" pageId="12" pageNumber="102" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B941B2FFFC4FFE6FF3D8175FDAAFDED" blockId="12.[189,513,613,640]" box="[189,513,613,640]" pageId="12" pageNumber="102">
<heading id="D0DCAC43FFC4FFE6FF3D8175FDAAFDED" bold="true" box="[189,513,613,640]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="12" pageNumber="102" reason="3">
<emphasis id="B95FC73DFFC4FFE6FF3D8175FDAAFDED" bold="true" box="[189,513,613,640]" pageId="12" pageNumber="102">Remarks and distribution</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B941B2FFFC4FFE6FF3D8187FE2CFC8A" blockId="12.[189,1399,660,792]" pageId="12" pageNumber="102">
Epigean species. This species shows a disjunct distribution so far. It is known from 
<collectingCountry id="F33C5BBFFFC4FFE6FB5A8187FA86FD3C" box="[1242,1325,660,686]" name="Russia" pageId="12" pageNumber="102">Russia</collectingCountry>
, from 
<collectingRegion id="49EFD5CDFFC4FFE6FF3D81A4FECDFD43" box="[189,358,695,721]" country="Russia" name="North Ossetia" pageId="12" pageNumber="102">North Ossetia</collectingRegion>
, near Alagir (
<typeStatus id="5490A58DFFC4FFE6FD8A81A4FD94FD43" box="[522,575,695,721]" pageId="12" pageNumber="102">type</typeStatus>
locality!), from 
<collectingRegion id="49EFD5CDFFC4FFE6FC8781A4FC51FD43" box="[775,1018,695,721]" country="Russia" name="Krasnodar" pageId="12" pageNumber="102">Krasnodar Province</collectingRegion>
, near Sochi and from 
<collectingRegion id="49EFD5CDFFC4FFE6FA8281A4FADDFD43" box="[1282,1398,695,721]" country="Russia" name="Stavropol'" pageId="12" pageNumber="102">Stavropol</collectingRegion>
Botanical Garden in 
<collectingRegion id="49EFD5CDFFC4FFE6FE4381C9FD19FD66" box="[451,690,730,756]" country="Russia" name="Stavropol'" pageId="12" pageNumber="102">Stavropol Province</collectingRegion>
. Also, it is known from the Mtskheta-Mtianeti region in 
<collectingCountry id="F33C5BBFFFC4FFE6FF3D81EEFEB6FC85" box="[189,285,765,791]" name="Georgia" pageId="12" pageNumber="102">Georgia</collectingCountry>
(
<figureCitation id="131007AAFFC4FFE6FEAE81EEFEDFFC8A" box="[302,372,765,792]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="3.[189,232,1981,2007]" captionTargetBox="[189,1398,1196,1938]" captionTargetId="figure-179@3.[189,1398,1196,1938]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="Fig. 1. Distribution of the genus Caucaseuma Strasser, 1970." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6564619" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6564619/files/figure.png" pageId="12" pageNumber="102">Fig. 1</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
